txt.en: Every day there is something to do during the Anniversary Festival.  Come and join everyone and participate in many Anniversary Festival activities for three days!
Waldo Rumble would like to thank you for your continued participation in the Anniversary Festival.
'You've celebrated for three whole days?! You might be even more excited for this year than I am!\n\n'Here, have a little reward I set aside just for you!'
'There are many rewards that await those who participate in the Anniversary Festival, and for those that celebrate for many days, the rewards are all the grander!'
Every year in the spring, the Anniversary Festival takes place to celebrate a very special occasion. Partake in the festivities to help mark this milestone with fireworks and good-cheer!
Every day there is something to do during the Anniversary Festival.  Come and join everyone and participate in many Anniversary Festival activities for three days!
